  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purposes of this study are to confirm that the Freedom Driver System is a suitable
      pneumatic driver for clinically stable TAH-t subjects, and that patients and lay caregivers
      can be trained to manage the Freedom Driver System safely outside the hospital.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
